{"tid":1308611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]星期六各區大部份巴士臨時取消前往北區運動場巴士站!?點撚算?","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T05:25:21.000Z","uid":255992,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"81cadaf113f83ff17a64e7078fbcafa002b629eb","tid":1308611,"uid":255992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:40:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">！！！！星期六光復上水遊行，14:00開始上水區大部分近火車/北區運動場巴士站會臨時取消，各路線會改道直至道路重開！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔洗怕，上水人幫大家整合已知受影響巴士線及影響後落車地點 <br />\n(有GOOGLE MAP 帶大家去集合地點, 落車地點及火車站亦會有指示牌)</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>火車站去集合地點路線</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=15BVNi7l5mzdrzOTnAWoERgY4zKSrPblj&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D15BVNi7l5mzdrzOTnAWoERgY4zKSrPblj%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=067ab6ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=15BVNi7l5mzdrzOTnAWoERgY4zKSrPblj&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>指示牌Sample</strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRUtzFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRUtzFV.jpg&h=fa22934c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UQHD7B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UQHD7B.jpg&h=8e8dda8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上水火車站至北區運動場 &ndash; 270 ＊停止服務＊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>中環(香港站) &ndash; 373 ,673 , 最近落車地點 &ldquo;翠麗花園&rdquo;</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1jhuC_Yc6R5pawcng2IbpuQnJYMg4D-_h&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1jhuC_Yc6R5pawcng2IbpuQnJYMg4D-_h%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=c173600d\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1jhuC_Yc6R5pawcng2IbpuQnJYMg4D-_h&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>佐敦(西九龍站) &ndash; W3 <br />\n荃灣如心廣場 &ndash; 278X (可到粉嶺站轉鐵)<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;太平總站&rdquo;  *落車地點變到好遠,自己行量,建議搭鐵</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=15CHi_nD2Uu6n8GWwcSFVP8IKlclU9yfM&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D15CHi_nD2Uu6n8GWwcSFVP8IKlclU9yfM%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=cb13cc21\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=15CHi_nD2Uu6n8GWwcSFVP8IKlclU9yfM&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>藍田 &ndash; 277E<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;天平村總站&rdquo;</ins>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Gjxfe8KPjg2DwymYRL_fk0ye0BhQ-KJv&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1Gjxfe8KPjg2DwymYRL_fk0ye0BhQ-KJv%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=4a48edef\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Gjxfe8KPjg2DwymYRL_fk0ye0BhQ-KJv&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>尖沙咀 &ndash; 270A<br />\n奧運站 &ndash; 270B<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;清河村&rdquo;  *尖沙咀人士建議搭鐵, 奧運站人士係清河村轉273B / 277E往天平村方向</ins><br />\n<br />\n<ins>青衣 &ndash; 279X<br />\n清河 &ndash; 273B<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;彩園路上水站&rdquo;  </ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1CB1V7Mw6fkJk3WpNZJKvL23rWajZddi-&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1CB1V7Mw6fkJk3WpNZJKvL23rWajZddi-%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=81ab40e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1CB1V7Mw6fkJk3WpNZJKvL23rWajZddi-&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>屯門 &ndash; 261 <br />\n天水圍 &ndash; 276,276P (改由天水圍出發)<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;寶石湖路&rdquo; (因寶石湖路係臨時站,未知確實站位,所以GOOGLE MAP只是粗略估計)</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1k9Va2ejpFA0h20ak2dOPS6za4grrKH1o&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1k9Va2ejpFA0h20ak2dOPS6za4grrKH1o%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=7c4309fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1k9Va2ejpFA0h20ak2dOPS6za4grrKH1o&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>元朗 &ndash; 77K<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;彩園總站&rdquo;</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Ten6s3reE92LXi-_Zi9a6Hq8et89ERqO&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1Ten6s3reE92LXi-_Zi9a6Hq8et89ERqO%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=30b88fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1Ten6s3reE92LXi-_Zi9a6Hq8et89ERqO&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>大埔/太和 &ndash; 73B<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;北區公園北門&rdquo; *落車地點變到好遠,自己行量,建議搭鐵</ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1PqP6ULLAgedTCjEirs4Owxryw-BO5oxL&amp;usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1PqP6ULLAgedTCjEirs4Owxryw-BO5oxL%26usp%3Dsharing&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Ney%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=93ec541b\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1PqP6ULLAgedTCjEirs4Owxryw-BO5oxL&amp;usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>沙頭角 &ndash; 78K<br />\n打鼓嶺 &ndash; 79K<br />\n最近落車地點 &ldquo;粉嶺站&rdquo;,請轉鐵<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺 &ndash; 273A *只入太平村,建議搭鐵<br />\n粉嶺 &ndash; 70K *天平總站及皇府山,建議搭鐵</ins><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">星期六黎上水既請睇以下兩個Post!!!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n星期六會入上水既入黎睇睇(逃走路線)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhotuS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhotuS</a><br />\n<br />\n[發夢] [詳細有圖] 夢見自己成為上水導遊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1306479\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1306479</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"e4bb3ff6d9bd320fd568b7f7741c9ca104100e57","tid":1308611,"uid":255992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:42:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9183023a1ef2d9d8de7afd68c43b4c1c875c6edc","tid":1308611,"uid":255992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"801ac05dda92171cf5f1edbce5d56cea12533e85","tid":1308611,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"134146f625c956592190ad1d1cf85045c8439b5d","tid":1308611,"uid":255992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"409629a35bb3a81180b3805b71c913ee3d186380","tid":1308611,"uid":255992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6244e85ec18275daf8720011f62bc9fc4446b980","tid":1308611,"uid":42108,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:48:46.000Z","msg":"推！阻唔到人去！"},{"pid":"248008f6e650a7a686d6f73fcbaf0ffbec986786","tid":1308611,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0d1c2044faac6a3782941f76103c3ccfaf79a91","tid":1308611,"uid":259255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bb9055216f2fda95d8c934cf28c792fafdf3d9c","tid":1308611,"uid":60398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:52:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n然後幾個一齊撲上去<br />\n各位識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p